ps://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNPeQ2w.jpg&h=f4a8a3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/suBXOPc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsuBXOPc.jpg&h=39c942dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EdP2ZVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEdP2ZVS.png&h=1bd9e71b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人會話法治已經死咗好撚耐<br />\n做呢啲嘢有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n我唔知道做咗又冇用<br />\n我淨係知唔做就一定乜嘢都冇<br />\n<br />\n之前情操高尚嗰條粉皮暫時都冇得再審政治案件<br />\n都係多得各位手足堅持寫信投訴<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果唔想香港好嘅社工越來越少<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n得返一啲淨係識得幫新賤民呃公屋嘅社畜<br />\n如果唔想香港未來<br />\n未成年手足被藍屍社工出賣</span></span><br />\n唔該一人一信<br />\n保護一個為咗愛我地而失去左一年光陰<br />\n為咗愛香港而冒着釘牌危機都要行出嚟<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好懶<br />\n依家輪到我哋愛佢了"},{"pid":"ca35f6e1372c294b6060af414f6df39c732fcd0a","tid":2068601,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e6dadfb97c136e19ac96ac6e78026a2c6f48bb3","tid":2068601,"uid":143343,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"8ac72b368e1ad5c6d2fa597413419a89714b42a5","tid":2068601,"uid":95138,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"8f8a0f38aabd2da7507c2d3804f8c74f8120deaa","tid":2068601,"uid":128923,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T21:04:41.000Z","msg":"唔係打中大 poly 根本唔會過得咁快"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T21:07:46.000Z","msg":"當日01風向叫人休息、等埋人權法<br />\n大家信晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T21:14:59.000Z","msg":"01背後班軍師差啲陰曬全香港人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T21:18:18.000Z","msg":"黨報01 what do u expect"},{"pid":"cb7a49a197e9c156f39fcc5e6939943ad65a7064","tid":2068601,"uid":95138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca35f6e1372c294b6060af414f6df39c732fcd0a","tid":2068601,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9e6dadfb97c136e19ac96a